casebody.data:
Mary Anne TAGOE, aka Mary Anne Roberts, petitioner,
v.
DISTRICT OF COLUMBIA DEPARTMENT OF EMPLOYMENT SERVICES, et al. No. 13-6892. Supreme Court of the United States June 9, 2014.

Case below, 62 A.3d 1283.

Motion of petitioner to add additional question to the petition for writ of certiorari denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the District of Columbia Court of Appeals denied.
